snippet.title: I Wanna Fly - Trailer (Nintendo)
snippet.description:
Features:

– an infinite world with uniquely designed, seamlessly transitioning stages
– over 20 different unlockable characters
– 10 ranks to achieve
– pixel art graphics

Coming 20/02/2019:
https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/i-wanna-fly-switch
